<section id="faq" class="py-24">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
    <div class="text-center mb-16 fade-up">
      <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">Frequently asked questions</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="space-y-4 fade-up" id="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span class="font-medium text-white">Can callers actually tell it's AI?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-dark-500 transition-transform faq-chevron" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-4 text-sm text-dark-400">
          <p>In our testing, over 90% of callers believe they're speaking to a human. Calva uses ElevenLabs' most natural voice AI with conversational speech patterns — it reacts emotionally, uses filler words, and adjusts its energy to match the caller. It's not your grandma's phone tree.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span class="font-medium text-white">How fast can I set this up?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-dark-500 transition-transform faq-chevron" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-4 text-sm text-dark-400">
          <p>5 minutes. Sign up, pick your industry template, customize your greeting and business info, and forward your phone. That's it. No IT department needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span class="font-medium text-white">What happens when I run out of minutes?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-dark-500 transition-transform faq-chevron" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-4 text-sm text-dark-400">
          <p>We'll notify you when you're approaching your limit. If you go over, calls still get answered — we'll never leave your customers hanging. Overages are billed at a reasonable per-minute rate, or you can upgrade your plan anytime.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span class="font-medium text-white">Can it handle complex conversations?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-dark-500 transition-transform faq-chevron" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-4 text-sm text-dark-400">
          <p>Yes. Calva is powered by advanced AI that understands context, handles follow-up questions, gives pricing estimates, and even handles emergencies with appropriate urgency. If a conversation needs a human, Calva transfers the call seamlessly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span class="font-medium text-white">Do I keep my existing phone number?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-dark-500 transition-transform faq-chevron" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-4 text-sm text-dark-400">
          <p>Absolutely. Just set up call forwarding from your existing number to your Calva number. Your customers call the same number they always have — Calva answers behind the scenes. We also provide a dedicated number if you prefer.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span class="font-medium text-white">Is there a contract?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-dark-500 transition-transform faq-chevron" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-4 text-sm text-dark-400">
          <p>No contracts, no commitments. Pay month to month. Cancel anytime from your dashboard. We keep you because you love the product, not because of fine print.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item glass rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <button class="w-full text-left px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">
          <span class="font-medium text-white">What about data privacy and security?</span>
          <svg class="w-5 h-5 text-dark-500 transition-transform faq-chevron" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M19 9l-7 7-7-7"/></svg>
        </button>
        <div class="faq-answer hidden px-6 pb-4 text-sm text-dark-400">
          <p>Your data is encrypted in transit and at rest. Call recordings and transcripts are only accessible to you. We're SOC 2 compliant and never sell or share your data. For healthcare businesses, we offer HIPAA-compliant configurations.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

